    "body": "@fvictorio the problem is solved with the optimizer switched off.\r\n\r\nUpdated example:\r\n\r\n```solidity\r\n// SPDX-License-Identifier: MIT\r\npragma solidity 0.8.17;\r\n\r\ncontract Test {\r\n  bool private flag = true;\r\n  \r\n  modifier someModifier() {\r\n    require(flag, \"Failed in modifier\");\r\n    _;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  function f() external someModifier {\r\n    require(false, \"Can't call this method\");\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\nWith optimizer switched on, stack trace has erroneous (superfluous) `someModifier` frame:\r\n\r\n```\r\n     Error: VM Exception while processing transaction: reverted with reason string 'Can't call this method'\r\n      at Test.someModifier (contracts/Test.sol:8)\r\n      at Test.f (contracts/Test.sol:12)\r\n      at processTicksAndRejections (node:internal/process/task_queues:96:5)\r\n```\r\n\r\nWith no code changes, but optimizer switched off:\r\n\r\n```\r\n     Error: VM Exception while processing transaction: reverted with reason string 'Can't call this method'\r\n      at Test.f (contracts/Test.sol:13)\r\n      at processTicksAndRejections (node:internal/process/task_queues:96:5)\r\n```",
